<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_272> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_271>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_272> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_272" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_202> ;
    del:text """Toleriranje takvoga, potpuno disfunkcionalnog pa i grotesknog modela s pravom naruÅ¡ava povjerenje Europljana u sustav, privlaÄi nezakonite migracije, a tragiÄni napadi muÅ¡karaca koji nisu imali pravo biti u Europi naglaÅ¡avaju i teÅ¡ke sigurnosne posljedice takvih trulih politika.
Bez uÄinkovitih povrataka, dobrovoljnih, ali i prisilnih, cijeli sustav migracija i azila gubi svaki smisao. Zato odluka o protjerivanju, odluka o neodobravanju azila mora imati konkretne posljedice ako Å¾elimo vladavinu prava i da se Europu, njezina pravila i njezine granice nikada viÅ¡e ne shvaÄa neozbiljno.
UvoÄenje stroÅ¾ih pravila, inovativnih ideja pa i deportacijskih centara izvan Europe nagradit Äe pakt o migraciji i azilu koji treba uvesti i uvest Äe viÅ¡e reda na europske granice. Sada njegova implementacija zato mora biti prioritet jer bez uÄinkovite migracijske politike koja ukljuÄuje i uÄinkovitu politiku povrataka nema vjerodostojne Europe.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T16:45:06"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_273> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_272>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_273> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_273" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_37> ;
    del:text "Time and time again, we have warned about the dangers of illegal migration, and time and time again we have been dismissed, ignored and vilified. How many more Europeans must die, be raped, robbed, attacked before you wake up? How many more grieving families must be left behind in sorrow and despair before we take this serious? For every victim, every shattered family, we must say: naÃ¯ve policies cost lives." ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T16:46:43"^^xsd:dateTime .

