<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_285> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_284>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_285> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_285" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_208> ;
    del:text """The new regulation needs to deliver effective, fast and coordinated returns. Like my colleague Lena DÃ¼pont pointed out today, those who are not entitled to stay on EU territory should be returned â it's simple as that. As expressed by Mr Commissioner, those who posed a threat should be returned, should be removed. I would add that prioritising the returns of those who pose a threat to our common security is key.
Improving the effectiveness and sustainability of the returns is one of the priorities of the Polish Presidency. Poland is supporting innovative solutions, including the concept of return hubs. But let's be clear efficiency cannot mean turning a blind eye to human rights and dignity. Let us be effective, but never forget our identity.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T17:03:17"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_286> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_285>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_286> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_286" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_209> ;
    del:text """Komise sice mluvÃ­ o moÅ¾nosti zpÅÃ­snit vÃ­zovou politiku nebo omezit obchodnÃ­ vÃ½hody, ale kde je povinnost tato opatÅenÃ­ skuteÄnÄ udÄlat? Kde je mechanismus, kterÃ½ by zajistil, Å¾e neochotnÃ© zemÄ okamÅ¾itÄ pocÃ­tÃ­ dÅ¯sledky svÃ©ho jednÃ¡nÃ­? Nikde. Bez automatickÃ½ch nekompromisnÃ­ch opatÅenÃ­ tento nÃ¡vrh opÄt skonÄÃ­ jako pouhÃ½ papÃ­r bez reÃ¡lnÃ©ho dopadu. EvropskÃ¡ komise mÄla jedineÄnou Å¡anci pÅijÃ­t s tvrdÃ½m, jasnÄ definovanÃ½m a vymahatelnÃ½m systÃ©mem sankcÃ­. MÃ­sto toho opÄt selhala. PÅedloÅ¾ila vÃ¡gnÃ­ plÃ¡n, kterÃ½ se dÃ¡ obejÃ­t, a my se pak budeme divit, Å¾e nÃ¡vraty stÃ¡le nefungujÃ­.
DÃ¡my a pÃ¡novÃ©, pokud tento nÃ¡vrh zÅ¯stane v tÃ©to podobÄ, nebude to ÅeÅ¡enÃ­, ale bude to jenom dalÅ¡Ã­ promarnÄnÃ¡ pÅÃ­leÅ¾itost.""" ;
