<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_342> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_341>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_342> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_342" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_246> ;
    del:text """Now, we must not only change our thinking and policies, but also defend Europe and our fellow Europeans. We must ensure European security, which is measured by the weakest link in its defence. Therefore, we must act together, not selectively. We must act now, not tomorrow.
Standardisation of weapons and military equipment, mobilisation of financial resources for their innovation, and speedy production and further development of military mobility and capabilities â these are the most important things now.
For the European defence community should involve our partners from the very beginning, especially candidate countries like Ukraine. Close cooperation in this area will undoubtedly benefit all participant countries and, most importantly, our citizens.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T18:32:10"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_343> a del:Contribution ;
