    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_256> ;
    del:text """Qui dit sÃ©curitÃ© des peuples dit aussi sÃ©curitÃ© sociale. DÃ©fense et sÃ©curitÃ© sociale vont de pair âÂ lutte contre la pauvretÃ©, logement, santÃ©, retraites, et jâen passeâ¦
Enfin, Monsieur le Commissaire, pensez-vous vraiment qu'il soit possible de construire une Europe de la dÃ©fense avec 27Â pays? Vu l'urgence, ne faudrait-il pas inciter un groupe restreint dâÃtats membres Ã  aller de lâavant Ã  ce sujet, comme nous lâavions fait pour Schengen?""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T18:49:42"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_356> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_355>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_356> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_356" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_257> ;
    del:text """Mums ir jÄizmanto tÄs priekÅ¡rocÄ«bas, ko sniedz Ukrainas aizsardzÄ«bas industrija â Ukrainas attÄ«stÄ«tÄs militÄrÄs tehnoloÄ£ijas jau ir pierÄdÄ«juÅ¡as sevi kaujas laukÄ. IepÄrkot bruÅojumu no Ukrainas, mÄs palÄ«dzam ne tikai tÄs ekonomikai, bet arÄ« investÄjam savÄ droÅ¡Ä«bÄ.
Aizdevuma plÄns ir iezÄ«mÄts Äetriem gadiem. Sagaidu, ka paredzÄtie un papildu finanÅ¡u avoti bÅ«s dalÄ«bvalstÄ«m pieejami tÅ«lÄ«tÄji, nevis kaut kad gada beigÄs.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T18:51:04"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_357> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_356>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_357> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_357" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_258> ;
    del:text """It's not about rearming individual countries, as in the Cold War. That would be insufficient, as it does not deter our adversaries. It is about collective rearming into an alliance which is able to compete with the deterrence that NATO had in the 1980s. That is the task.
For Europe, this requires delivering strategic enablers to operate on a divisional level, Commissioner, and the majority of those enablers are currently being paid for and operated by the US, which is still our ally. But Europe needs to develop or buy such enablers ourselves now.
Secondly, continental Europe is much bigger than the European Union. So the solution when it comes to a solid security architecture should, therefore, also include the UK, Norway, Turkey, Iceland, even Canada in a European security council â of which nothing has been mentioned. The industrial policy in the white paper should follow this security architecture. I ask you to take this on board, dear Commissioner, and get it right this time.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T18:52:29"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_358> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_357>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_358> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_358" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_259> ;
    del:text """Trump e Putin ridono della nostra disorganizzazione e ci impongono le loro regole: un'Europa sempre piÃ¹ povera, disorganizzata, priva di una governance politica e una difesa comune Ã¨ ciÃ² che vogliono e che gli stiamo consegnando con la nostra idea di difesa: 800 miliardi per 27 eserciti, senza una missione comune e senza vaglio del Parlamento.
PiÃ¹ sicurezza Ã¨ una governance unica e democratica, non 27; interoperabilitÃ , non altre armi; infrastrutture, diritti, welfare e rinnovabili, non tagliare questi investimenti; diplomazia, corpi di pace, nuovi alleati, non escalation dei conflitti.
Nasciamo per costruire la pace: non sono le nostre armi a fare paura ma il nostro potenziale come unione politica, federale e democratica. Spinelli diceva: un'Europa unita Ã¨ il miglior modo per garantire libertÃ  e pace.
(L'oratrice accetta di rispondere a una domanda "cartellino blu")""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T18:53:54"^^xsd:dateTime .

