Schriftliche ErklÃ¤rungen (Artikel 178)""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T22:31:05"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_523> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_521>,
