    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_218> ;
    del:text """Svaret Ã¤r att kapitulation inte ligger i deras intresse utifrÃ¥n det lÃ¥ngsiktiga mÃ¥let att utrota Israel. Svaret Ã¤r att de inte oroar sig fÃ¶r Gazas civila, som de frÃ¤mst ser som civila skÃ¶ldar som kan offras i kampen mot Israel. SÃ¥ lÃ¤nge som dessa omstÃ¤ndigheter kvarstÃ¥r kommer ingen lÃ¥ngvarig fred att kunna uppnÃ¥s. DÃ¤rfÃ¶r behÃ¶ver EU Ã¶ka trycket pÃ¥ palestinierna och deras ledare i sÃ¥vÃ¤l Gaza som pÃ¥ VÃ¤stbanken, genom att villkora bistÃ¥ndet och rikta sanktioner mot Hamas ekonomiska struktur.
Den palestinska myndigheten behÃ¶ver i handling ta avstÃ¥nd frÃ¥n Hamas, och Gaza demilitariseras. Det palestinska folket behÃ¶ver inse att vÃ¤gen till fred fÃ¶rutsÃ¤tter ett totalt avstÃ¥ndstagande frÃ¥n terrorism.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T23:02:48"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_542> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_541>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_542> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_542" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_73> ;
    del:text """Para pressionar, Israel cortou todo o fornecimento de eletricidade a Gaza (o que tambÃ©m impede o acesso a Ã¡gua potÃ¡vel dessalinizada) e suspendeu toda a entrada de ajuda humanitÃ¡ria.
NÃ³s nÃ£o podemos continuar a assistir passivamente Ã  degradaÃ§Ã£o da vida em Gaza. Israel tem de voltar a permitir a entrada de ajuda humanitÃ¡ria â que nÃ£o Ã© um instrumento de pressÃ£o sobre o Hamas, mas um direito da populaÃ§Ã£o civil de Gaza.
O prolongamento da guerra em Gaza sÃ³ serve os interesses polÃ­ticos e pessoais de Netanyahu, apoiado por uma coligaÃ§Ã£o de extremaâdireita ultraortodoxa. As desrespeitosas propostas da administraÃ§Ã£o Trump para o territÃ³rio sÃ³ reforÃ§am esta lideranÃ§a, que estÃ¡ cada vez mais longe de representar todos os israelitas.
As feridas de dÃ©cadas sÃ³ comeÃ§arÃ£o a sarar se construirmos uma soluÃ§Ã£o baseada em dois Estados e em direitos iguais para israelitas e palestinianos. E, para isso, Israel e o Hamas precisam de voltar a avanÃ§ar imediatamente para cumprir as fases subsequentes do acordo de cessarâfogo.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T23:04:09"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_543> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_542>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_543> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_543" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_377> ;
    del:text """Y mientras tanto, Â¿quÃ© estÃ¡ haciendo Europa, seÃ±ora comisaria? Â¿Mirar hacia otro lado para contentar a Trump? Â¿El mismo Trump que acaba de detener a un estudiante palestino en la Universidad de Columbia para impedir que pueda expresarse libremente y seguir intentando que no se cumplan los derechos humanos ni en Gaza ni en los Estados Unidos?
SeÃ±orÃ­as, los valores europeos no son solo un eslogan, se tienen que cumplir cada dÃ­a y, para ello, debemos proteger los derechos humanos en Gaza, aumentar la ayuda humanitaria, hacer misiones de paz y construir, de verdad, la paz en todo el mundo.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T23:05:26"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_544> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_543>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_544> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_544" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_22> ;
    del:text """Câest lÃ , la caractÃ©ristique de cette Union europÃ©enne, aujourdâhui: un mÃ©pris pour la vie des Palestiniens! Parce que oui, vous avez rÃ©ussi Ã  faire un discours en disant: Â«Ah! La situation Ã  Gaza empireâ¦Â», sans mentionner pourquoi elle empire. Pourquoi est-ce quâelle empire? Eh bien, parce quâIsraÃ«l bloque toute aide humanitaire, toute nourriture, et mÃªme lâÃ©lectricitÃ©. Quâest-ce que cela veut dire? Sans Ã©lectricitÃ©, pas de dÃ©salinisation de lâeau, et donc pas dâeau potable. Ainsi, les gens, les familles, les enfants nâont pas dâeau potable, et vous, vous Ãªtes lÃ  en train de rigoler! Comment est-ce possible, Monsieur le Ministre? Comment est-ce possible, sâil vous plaÃ®t?
Alors, aujourdâhui, cette complicitÃ© europÃ©enne et ce manque de respect pour la vie des Palestiniens doivent cesser, parce que cela va se payer cash! Je vous le promets!""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T23:06:49"^^xsd:dateTime .

<https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_545> a del:Contribution ;
    del:follows <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_544>,
        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_545> ;
    del:identifier "contribution_545" ;
    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_378> ;
    del:text "I believe the EU should push for a twoâstate solution and challenge its biggest ally. Now, more than ever, we should act independently from the United States in order to stop the genocide of Palestinians and finally achieve a twoâstate solution." ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-11T23:08:02"^^xsd:dateTime .

