    del:madeBy <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_379> ;
    del:text """The recent obstruction of a European Parliament delegation and the deportation of MEPs and EU officials is an affront to our democratic processes, and I want to express my solidarity to my constituency colleague and Chair of the delegation, Lynn Boylan. You mess with one Dub; you mess with all Dubs! We stand with you, Lynn, in demanding the strongest possible response from President Metsola.
