        <https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_113> ;
    del:text "",
        """We must bolster Moldova's resilience now. This is about more than financial aid. It is about resilience, reforms and Moldova's EU path. Strengthening institutions, independent media and electoral integrity must be immediate, not gradual.
The first payout is set at 20Â %, but in this critical moment, that's not enough. We should amend the plan and increase it by an additional 5Â %. Moving faster and further sends a clear message: Moldova belongs in Europe, free from malign influence.""" ;
    del:timestamp "2025-03-10T20:51:05"^^xsd:dateTime,
